TopicTitle: Updated Nvidia Drivers, now KSP crashes after loading

Articles.Content:
Hello.

My KSP client, although heavily modded, ran perfectly fine. I updated my Nvidia Drivers, and now it refuses to transition between full loading and the menu animation starting up. 

Here is the output log: http://www.mediafire.com/file/mjds7lbystd2ndn/output_log.txt

**** Crash! ****

I have never seen a crash log reference the system32 folder of my windows install! What could be the problem?

Question .... is there perhaps a 32 bit nvidia driver and 64 bit driver?

If so then it could be possible that all the system32 references are being caused by trying to run 64 bit KSP with drivers aimed at 32

Just a though ... I could be totally off base but might be something to look into

I had the same happen to me a few days ago.  Rolled back the driver and everything was cool.

Wasn't just KSP, I had other programs that quick working.
